<plot>Duff McKagan is the legendary bass player for Velvet Revolver and formerly Guns N' Roses. Duff gives an intimate behind-the scenes look at his life as a professional musician - including rare photos and video footage. Duff then gives in-depth bass lessons for how to play "Slither" and "Set Me Free" by Velvet Revolver and jams the tracks with Jane's Addiction drummer Stephen Perkins.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063795</url></doc>
